defaultPlease see photograph  number 3 taken in April this year and notice the damage to the walls. The grass verges have all been eroded and vehicles are now damaging the foundation stones. There is more anxiety felt
default 
defaultby the walkers and cyclists and it is reported that it is
default 
defaultnot only the horse riders who feel prohibited but also walkers and cyclists.
